OL,3,CMan convicted of killing girlfriend in
OL,4,Cscalding bath walks free
OL,6,FA man who was found guilty of gross
OL,7,Fnegligence manslaughter for leaving
OL,8,Fhis parter to die after she was
OL,9,Fscalded in a bath has avoided jail
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FMark Clowes, 53, from Audley in , ran
OL,13,Fthe boiling hot bath for 43-year-old
OL,14,FClare Bell at 11am on 9 August 2020.
OL,16,FHe then helped her out of it as she
OL,17,Fhad been drinking, police said.
