OL,3,CMan convicted of killing girlfriend in
OL,4,Cscalding bath walks free
OL,6,FIt would have been obvious to Clowes
OL,7,Fthat Ms Bell had suffered serious
OL,8,Fscald injuries in the incident as he
OL,9,Flater told a paramedic that "he saw
OL,10,Fthat her skin had shed from her feet".
OL,12,FHe then didn't check on his partner
OL,13,Ffor hours, or call an ambulance,
OL,14,Fdespite knowing she would have been
OL,15,Fincapable of doing it herself.
OL,17,FMore than six hours later at 5.10pm,
OL,18,FClowes rang 999 - but Ms Bell, who was
OL,19,Ffound on their bed, was already dead.
