OL,6,FDuring his sentencing, High Court
OL,7,FJudge Mr Justice Calver said: "I
OL,8,Faccept your gross negligent conduct
OL,9,Fwas a lapse in your otherwise loving
OL,10,Fcare. I consider this to be an
OL,11,Fexceptional case.
OL,13,F"This is a very sad case. Clare's
OL,14,Fdeath has had and continues to have a
OL,15,Ftraumatic effect on members of her
OL,16,Ffamily.
OL,18,F"You are a functioning alcoholic.
OL,19,FClare was not only an alcoholic. She
OL,20,Fwas suffering from alcohol
OL,21,Fketoacidosis.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
