OL,6,F"Her death is as tragic and
OL,7,Funnecessary as that of anybody who is
OL,8,Fkilled."
OL,10,FClowes was sentenced to two years in
OL,11,Fprison, suspended for two years, with
OL,12,Fan alcohol treatment requirement for
OL,13,Fthree months and a rehabilitation
OL,14,Factivity requirement for 60 days.
OL,16,FShe had 30% full-thickness burns -
OL,17,Fwith extensive scalding to her back,
OL,18,Fbottom, thighs, feet, arms and elbows.
