OL,6,FThese brutal injuries were consistent
OL,7,Fwith being in a very hot bath - and
OL,8,Fthe pathologist said that the scalding
OL,9,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Cheryl
OL,12,FHannan said: "Clare should have been
OL,13,Fable to trust Mark to look after her
OL,14,Fwhen she was incapable. He didn't do
OL,15,Fanything for Clare until it was too
OL,16,Flate.
OL,18,F"We employed a number of different
OL,19,Fexperts to determine what took place
OL,20,Fthat day.
